<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Entrar · Metavis</title>

  <style>
    /* ===== Aeonik Pro Font Face ===== */
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Regular.ttf') format('truetype'),
           url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Regular.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Medium.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 500; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Bold.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro';
      src: url('/fonts/aeonik/AeonikPro-Black.otf') format('opentype');
      font-weight: 900; font-style: normal; font-display: swap;
    }
  </style>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --azul-petroleo:      #01192B;
      --azul-dark:          #010f1a;
      --azul-light:         #0d2d45;
      --laranja:            #EE6D07;
      --laranja-dark:       #c95a00;
      --cinza-claro:        #F4F6F8;
      --cinza-medio:        #A5B3BB;
      --preto-carvao:       #111827;
      --branco:             #FFFFFF;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Aeonik Pro', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--azul-dark);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    /* Layout de duas colunas */
    .login-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
      min-height: 540px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    /* Coluna esquerda - branding */
    .login-brand {
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--azul-petroleo);
      padding: 48px 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .login-brand::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px; right: -60px;
      width: 220px; height: 220px;
      background: var(--laranja);
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.08;
      filter: blur(40px);
    }

    .login-brand::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -40px; left: -40px;
      width: 160px; height: 160px;
      background: var(--laranja);
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: 0.06;
      filter: blur(50px);
    }

    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--branco);
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .brand-logo span { color: var(--laranja); }

    .brand-content { position: relative; }

    .brand-content h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--branco);
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .brand-content p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .brand-pills {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .brand-pill {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    }

    .brand-pill-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--laranja);
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* Coluna direita - formulário */
    .login-form-side {
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--branco);
      padding: 48px 44px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .login-form-side h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--azul-petroleo);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .login-form-side .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--cinza-medio);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .form-group { margin-bottom: 18px; }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--preto-carvao);
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }

    .form-group input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 1.5px solid #E5E7EB;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: inherit;
      color: var(--preto-carvao);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      background: var(--cinza-claro);
    }

    .form-group input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--azul-petroleo);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15,42,61,0.1);
      background: var(--branco);
    }

    .btn-login {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--azul-petroleo);
      color: var(--branco);
      border: none;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .btn-login:hover {
      background: var(--azul-light);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(15,42,61,0.2);
    }

    .btn-login:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .login-footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--cinza-medio);
    }

    .login-footer a {
      color: var(--laranja);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .login-footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .back-link {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .back-link a {
      color: var(--cinza-medio);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .back-link a:hover { color: var(--azul-petroleo); }

    /* Alerta de erro */
    .alert-error {
      background: #fef2f2;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      color: #b91c1c;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .alert-error::before {
      content: '⚠';
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    /* Responsivo */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .login-brand { display: none; }
      .login-wrapper { max-width: 420px; border-radius: 16px; }
      .login-form-side { padding: 36px 28px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="login-wrapper">

    <!-- Branding -->
    <div class="login-brand">
      <!-- Glass cube decorativo -->
      <img src="/images/branding/metavis-glass-cube-01.png"
           alt=""
           draggable="false"
           style="position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; opacity:0.15; pointer-events:none; user-select:none;">

      <a href="/" class="brand-logo" style="display:flex; align-items:center;">
        <img src="/images/logos/Metavis%20-%20Logotipo%20-%20Branco.png"
             alt="Metavis"
             style="height: 26px; object-fit: contain;"
             onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline';">
        <span style="display:none;">Metavis<span>.</span></span>
      </a>

      <div class="brand-content">
        <h2>Inteligência<br/>organizacional<br/>real.</h2>
        <p>Analise a estrutura da sua empresa com profundidade e tome decisões baseadas em evidências.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="brand-pills">
        <div class="brand-pill">
          <span class="brand-pill-dot"></span>
          Dados isolados por empresa
        </div>
        <div class="brand-pill">
          <span class="brand-pill-dot"></span>
          Análises em minutos
        </div>
        <div class="brand-pill">
          <span class="brand-pill-dot"></span>
          Zero configuração técnica
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Formulário -->
    <div class="login-form-side">
      <h1>Bem-vindo de volta</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Entre com suas credenciais para acessar a plataforma.</p>

      <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
        <div class="alert-error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/auth/login" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">E-mail</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="seu@email.com" required autocomplete="email" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="senha">Senha</label>
          <input type="password" id="senha" name="senha" placeholder="••••••••" required autocomplete="current-password" />
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-login">Entrar na plataforma</button>
      </form>

      <div class="back-link">
        <a href="/">← Voltar para o início</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
